    "en": {
      "title": "I am not a friend of the Rajapaksa people but a friend of the people",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "President Ranil Wickramasinghe said that he is not a friend of the Rajapaksas but a friend of the people.",
        "Mr. Ranil Wickramasinghe said this while answering the questions asked by the journalists after coming out of the Hunupitiya Gangarama temple in Colombo after taking the oath of office.",
        "Mr. Wickramasinghe said that he worked with the Rajapaksas and they are not his friends."
      ],
